      • close

        public final void close()
        Closes parser: * closes (and nulls) underlying stream * nulls dynamic data * moves object to 'closed' state, where methods return invalid values and next() throws IOException.

      • next

        public final int next()
               throws IOException
        Advances to the next tag. Once method returns END_DOCUMENT, it always returns END_DOCUMENT. Once method throws an exception, it always throws the same exception.
        Throws:
        IOException
